NK039(ti)020:1: // dpal ldan lha mo'i bskang mdos bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)020:2: dpal ldan lha mo'i bskang mdos kyi bca' thabs zhes bya ba ni /
NK039(ti)020:3: dpal chen he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK039(ti)020:4: dpal ldan lha mo'i bskang mdos 'di ni /
NK039(ti)020:5: sngags pa dam tshig nyams pa dang /
NK039(ti)020:6: nad tshab chen po phog gam /
NK039(ti)020:7: yi dwags chen po lus zhugs gam /
NK039(ti)020:8: gdon bgegs bkra mi shis pa byung na 'di la mdos bya /
NK039(ti)020:9: lha bsnyen ci rigs pa la sogs te /
NK039(ti)020:11: de yang lha mo'i bsnyen pa gong du song nas /
NK039(ti)020:12: mchod rdzas yo byad bsags pa ni /
NK039(ti)020:19: me tog tshogs par bya la /
NK039(ti)020:22: gtor ma stod zur gsum pa gcig pa legs par bya la ngos gcig pad+ma rak+ta'am mtshal gyis byugah /
NK039(ti)020:23: ngos gcig kha de zhing chen dkar po bya /
NK039(ti)020:24: ngos gcig ka dur sol gyi byug /
NK039(ti)020:25: ngos gsum du lug nag bdun /
NK039(ti)020:28: bshos bu'i rtse mo la lha mo'i 'od zer ser po bzhin /
NK039(ti)020:29: phyag na khram phyes kyi shed gtor bya bre la bzhag go //
NK039(ti)020:30: de bya ba dpon sor gsum byas la btsugs /
NK039(ti)020:31: de'i steng du dar nag gdugs phub /
NK039(ti)020:32: nam mkha' mthing nag gcig btsugs /
NK039(ti)020:33: de'i phyi rim ye shes mkha' 'gro bcu bzhi la lug bcu bzhi /
NK039(ti)020:34: dman mo lnga bcu rtsa brgyad la bya lnga bcu rtsa brgyad /
NK039(ti)020:35: dbyings kyi yum drug la lcong khra drug /
NK039(ti)020:36: de'i rgyab tu 'byung po'i lo skor bcu gnyis /
NK039(ti)020:37: gtor ma'i rtse mo la dpal ldan lha mo bong bu la bcib pa /
NK039(ti)020:38: g.yas su ba lam dril nag la zhon pa /
NK039(ti)020:39: g.yon du khri sman ma bya mo la bcib pa /
NK039(ti)020:40: rgyab tu skyi mthing sha ba la zhon pa /
NK039(ti)020:42: bye brag gi rtse mor gzug go //
NK039(ti)020:44: rngogs chags rnams rtsa bar gzug go //
NK039(ti)020:46: de 'dra ba'i gzugs 'gros thams cad tshang bar bya'o //
NK039(ti)020:54: la sogs te mda' dar yo byad thams cad tshang bar bya la /
NK039(ti)020:55: bskang tshogs spyi dang mthun par bya'o //
NK039(ti)020:57: khrus gsol mchod rdzas byin gyis rlabs la /
NK039(ti)020:58: yi dam gyi nga rgyal dang ldan pa'i 'di skad do //
NK039(ti)020:60: dpal ldan thugs dam gnyen po bskul //
NK039(ti)020:61: thugs dam gnyen po mi bskul du //
NK039(ti)020:63: btsan btsun kun la bka' nan chung //
NK039(ti)020:64: da ni dpal ldan khyod la tshang bag lo //
NK039(ti)020:65: khyod kyi cho la nga re mkhas //
NK039(ti)020:66: nam mkha'i khams la bzhugs tsam na //
NK039(ti)020:67: sems can skye shi la ma ston ma //
NK039(ti)020:68: de yang byang shar re ma ti //
NK039(ti)020:69: dmar chen gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)020:70: yon bdag glud byol dgra la thongs //
NK039(ti)020:71: gnod byed bar chad bgegs la thong //
NK039(ti)020:72: ri rab zam la bzhugs pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:74: klu rgyal kun gyi dgyes sde ma //
NK039(ti)020:75: klu bran kun gyi gtso mo mdzad //
NK039(ti)020:76: de yang byang shar dmar chen gtor ma yon bdag
NK039(ti)020:77: glud byol gnod byed bar chad ma bdun gtso mo
NK039(ti)020:78: mdzad tsam na // rdo rje dkar mo dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)020:79: gsang sngags 'chang gi bka' nyan ma //
NK039(ti)020:80: de yang byang shar dmar chen yon bdag gnod byed rta mgrin gzungs ma mdzad pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:81: bar snang khams la khyab par 'phyo //
NK039(ti)020:82: de yang byang shar dmar chen yon bdag gnod pa'i srin mo bzhi'i gtso mo mdzad pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:83: dkar mo nyi ma'i spyan gcig ma //
NK039(ti)020:84: gling bzhi mgyogs ma lha'i sring //
NK039(ti)020:85: de yang byang shar dmar chen yon bdag gnod pa'i srin mo bdun cu'i pho mo'i gtso mo mdzad //
NK039(ti)020:86: gnod byed srog 'phrog srin mo 'khrung 'khrung mo //
NK039(ti)020:87: brgya'i gtso mo las mkhan ma //
NK039(ti)020:88: de yang dmar chen yon bdag gnod pa'i brtan ma bcu gnyis gtso mo mdzad //
NK039(ti)020:89: ma btsun ug chos dbyar mo sil //
NK039(ti)020:90: dkyil 'khor skyong bar khas blang pas //
NK039(ti)020:91: de yang dmar chen yon bdag gnod pa'i bzlog byed ma'i dus la bab //
NK039(ti)020:92: bzlog go dmar chen gtor mas bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:93: mtshan zhing dur khrod gnas su nyul //
NK039(ti)020:95: rnal 'byor dam tshig gtsang mi gtsang //
NK039(ti)020:96: mched lcam brtse gdung che'am chung //
NK039(ti)020:97: slob dpon ting 'dzin drod nyul ma //
NK039(ti)020:98: legs nyes gnyis kyi stong 'dzin cing //
NK039(ti)020:99: dam tshig nyams pa'i rjes gcod ma //
NK039(ti)020:100: nyid kyi sku mdog nag po la //
NK039(ti)020:101: ral pa nag po gting zab bkang //
NK039(ti)020:102: ral bu'i zar bu g.yas nas g.yon du 'khyil //
NK039(ti)020:103: kha nas mi khrag rta khrag 'dzag /
NK039(ti)020:104: mig nas khrag 'dzag zu lu lu //
NK039(ti)020:105: drel rta nag gsum spyad pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:106: dpag tshad brgyad khri bzhi stong yang //
NK039(ti)020:107: yud tsam mtshan mo gcig gis khyab //
NK039(ti)020:108: rnal 'byor chen mo a la la //
NK039(ti)020:109: dbang phyug chen mo a la la //
NK039(ti)020:110: khyod kyi lag pa g.yas pa nas //
NK039(ti)020:111: bdud kyi khram bam nam mkhar phyar //
NK039(ti)020:112: skye 'gro'i gzugs su snang ba kun //
NK039(ti)020:113: sang phod deng sang su 'chi ba //
NK039(ti)020:114: do tshigs khyod kyi khram la thob //
NK039(ti)020:116: sku glud gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)020:117: bdud kyi khram kha da phyes shig /
NK039(ti)020:118: khyod kyi lag pa g.yon pa nas //
NK039(ti)020:119: btsan gyi shwo rdil dkar nag bkram //
NK039(ti)020:120: shwo la mi theb mi srid kyis //
NK039(ti)020:121: shwo la bab par gyur pa na //
NK039(ti)020:123: srog glud gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)020:124: btsan gyi shwa d+hil da gtor cig /
NK039(ti)020:125: khyod kyi mchan khung g.yon pa nas //
NK039(ti)020:126: byang dmar dkyus kyi bam po rbed //
NK039(ti)020:127: skye 'gro'i gzugs su snang ba kun //
NK039(ti)020:128: sang phod deng song su 'chi ba //
NK039(ti)020:129: do tshigs khyod kyi khram la 'debs //
NK039(ti)020:131: srog glud gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)020:132: byang dmar dkyus kyi bam po rbed //
NK039(ti)020:133: khyod kyi mchan khung g.yon pa nas //
NK039(ti)020:134: nad kyi rkyal pa sngon dmar la //
NK039(ti)020:135: sbrul nag lnga brgya'i kha 'ching can //
NK039(ti)020:136: nad yams de ni dgra la gtor //
NK039(ti)020:137: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK039(ti)020:138: gsang sngags 'bras bu'i chos dar te //
NK039(ti)020:139: rnal 'byor grong bsnyen dar dus la //
NK039(ti)020:140: dge sdig 'chol bar spyad dus la //
NK039(ti)020:142: de tshe khyod kyi bstan pa dar //
NK039(ti)020:143: de tshe srid pa'i ma mo 'khrug /
NK039(ti)020:144: ma mo 'khrug pa'i rtags yin pas //
NK039(ti)020:145: bzhi brgya rtsa bzhi'i nad rnams dang //
NK039(ti)020:146: ye 'grogs sum brgya drug cu dang //
NK039(ti)020:147: glo bur brgyad cu rtsa gcig byung //
NK039(ti)020:148: dus min 'chi ba rnam brgyad dad //
NK039(ti)020:149: nad kyang ma mo khyod kyi nad //
NK039(ti)020:150: khrag kyang ma mo khyod kyi khrag /
NK039(ti)020:151: rims kyang ma mo khyod kyis rims //
NK039(ti)020:152: de ring yon bdag 'khor bcas kyi //
NK039(ti)020:153: srog glud gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)020:154: nad kyi rkyal pa kha ching la //
NK039(ti)020:155: mtshon gyi gru gu slar rdog cig /
NK039(ti)020:156: nad kha chod la rims kha bsgyur //
NK039(ti)020:157: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK039(ti)020:158: gsang sngags bon ltar gyer ba dang //
NK039(ti)020:159: dge sdig 'chol bar spyod pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:160: dpal ldan lha mo thugs 'khros pas //
NK039(ti)020:161: kha rlangs ser po btang ba'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:162: bud med nag mo sa gzhi gang //
NK039(ti)020:163: nad kyis na bun sprin ltar gtib //
NK039(ti)020:164: de tshe mtshon gyi bskal pa dar //
NK039(ti)020:165: skrang pa g.yan pa shu ba dang //
NK039(ti)020:166: mdze nad rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)020:167: nad kyang ma mo khyod kyi nad //
NK039(ti)020:168: khrag kyang mo mo khyod rims kyang ma mo de
NK039(ti)020:169: ring yon bdag srog glud gtor ma mtshon gyi gru'u
NK039(ti)020:170: mi dang glud du da rjes shig /
NK039(ti)020:171: nad kha chod la rims kha bsgyur //
NK039(ti)020:172: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK039(ti)020:173: gsang sngags 'bras bu'i chos dar te //
NK039(ti)020:174: rnal 'byor grong bsnyen dar ba dang //
NK039(ti)020:175: gsang sngags bon ltar gyer ba dang /
NK039(ti)020:176: dge sdig 'chol bar spyod pa na //
NK039(ti)020:177: dpal ldan lha mo thugs khros nas //
NK039(ti)020:178: bud med ser pos sa gzhi gang //
NK039(ti)020:179: mkha' la nad sprin ser po chags //
NK039(ti)020:180: che bzhi mkhris pas bsha' ya btang //
NK039(ti)020:181: sha ser khrag ser mig kyang ser //
NK039(ti)020:182: rgya nad thams cad de la byung //
NK039(ti)020:183: nad kyang ma mo khrag kyang ma mo rims kyang
NK039(ti)020:184: de ring srog glud nad kyi mtshon gyi dmar chen
NK039(ti)020:185: gtor ma nad kha chod la rims kha bsgyur //
NK039(ti)020:186: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK039(ti)020:187: gsang sngags 'bras bu chos dar tshe //
NK039(ti)020:188: rnal 'byor grong bsnyen dar dus la //
NK039(ti)020:189: dge sdig 'chol ba spyad dus la //
NK039(ti)020:191: de tshe khyod kyi bstan pa dar //
NK039(ti)020:192: dpal ldan lha mo khyod khros nas //
NK039(ti)020:193: kha rlang dmar po btang ba'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:194: bud med dmar mos sa gzhi gang //
NK039(ti)020:195: mkha' la nad sprin dmar po chags //
NK039(ti)020:196: de tshe nad kyi bskal pa dar //
NK039(ti)020:197: rims nad tsha ba sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)020:198: khyug nad rgyu gzer sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)020:199: khrag tu skyug pa sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)020:200: nad kyang ma mo khrag kyang rims kyang bdag dang yon bdag srog glud /
NK039(ti)020:201: nad kyi mtshon gyi dmar chen gtor ma nad kha chod la lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK039(ti)020:202: gsang sngags rnal 'byor grong gsang sngags bon ltar gyer ba dang //
NK039(ti)020:203: dpal ldan lha mo khyod khros nas //
NK039(ti)020:204: kha rlang smug po btang ba'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:205: bud med smug pos sa gzhi gang //
NK039(ti)020:206: mkha' la nad sprin smug po chags //
NK039(ti)020:207: dar nag ru mtshon thigs se thib //
NK039(ti)020:208: phyag na mdung dmar chims se chim //
NK039(ti)020:209: ba dan smug po lhubs se lhub //
NK039(ti)020:210: sku la go mtshon ya la la //
NK039(ti)020:211: dug gi 'khrug pa bslang bar byed //
NK039(ti)020:212: mtshon gyi char pa 'beb par byed //
NK039(ti)020:213: khyod la mthun pa'i rdzas 'bul ba //
NK039(ti)020:214: dmar chen gtor ma sgrub mchog bdag dang yon bdag la //
NK039(ti)020:215: 'khrugs pa'i bskal pa zhi bar mdzod //
NK039(ti)020:216: mtshon gyi bskal pa zhi bar mdzod //
NK039(ti)020:217: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK039(ti)020:218: gsang sngags 'bras bu rnal 'byor grong gsang sngags bon ltar dge sdig 'chol bar spyad dus la //
NK039(ti)020:219: dpal ldan lha mo khyod khros nas //
NK039(ti)020:220: kha rlang nag po btang bud med nag mos sa gzhi gang //
NK039(ti)020:221: nad kyi na bun nag po 'khrigs //
NK039(ti)020:222: de tshe mtshon gyis bskal pa dar //
NK039(ti)020:223: lhog pa dkar nag 'bum nag dang //
NK039(ti)020:224: skrangs dang g.yan pa shu ba dang //
NK039(ti)020:225: mdze nad rnam pa sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)020:226: nad kyang ma mo khyod kyis nad //
NK039(ti)020:227: khrag kyang ma mo rims kyang bdag dang yon srog
NK039(ti)020:228: glud gtor ma nad kyi rkyal mtshon gyi bskal ba
NK039(ti)020:229: dmar chen gtor ma bdag dang yon bdag nad kha
NK039(ti)020:231: lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK039(ti)020:232: gsang sngags 'bras bu rnal 'byor grong bsnyen dge sdig 'chol bar spyad dus la //
NK039(ti)020:233: gsang sngags bon ltar dpal ldan lha mo thugs khros nas //
NK039(ti)020:234: kha rlang dkar po btang ba dang //
NK039(ti)020:235: bud med dkar mos sa gzhi gang //
NK039(ti)020:236: mkha' la nad kyi sprin ltar gtib //
NK039(ti)020:237: de tshe nad kyi bskal pa dar //
NK039(ti)020:238: rlung nag 'tshub ma mu ge dang //
NK039(ti)020:239: thog dang ser ba shwa bud dang //
NK039(ti)020:240: dus ma yin par 'chi ba'i nad //
NK039(ti)020:241: nad kyang ma mo khrag kyang rims kyang ma rgyu
NK039(ti)020:242: sbyor yon bdag srog glud nad kyi rkyal mtshon gyi
NK039(ti)020:243: bskal mi dang glud du da barje la //
NK039(ti)020:244: nad kha chod gsang sngags spyod grangs mang po yang //
NK039(ti)020:245: gzhung ltar spyod pa nor grang la //
NK039(ti)020:246: bka' ltar spyod pa dbang phyug bdag /
NK039(ti)020:247: man ngag thugs dam rgyud bskul nas //
NK039(ti)020:248: bdag cag rnal 'byor bsgrub pa po //
NK039(ti)020:249: dpal chen bdud rtsi rnam lnga mchod //
NK039(ti)020:250: lus dang grib ma bzhin du mchod //
NK039(ti)020:251: gsur chen dud pas rgyun mi chad //
NK039(ti)020:252: dbang phyug phu nas gus 'debs kyi //
NK039(ti)020:253: dpal ldan mda' na snyan ma sra //
NK039(ti)020:254: ri lung med par gu yi thobs //
NK039(ti)020:255: dbang phyug mda' na g.yab dor cig /
NK039(ti)020:256: dpal ldan phu na spyan ma rdul //
NK039(ti)020:257: nag mo mang po'i nam mkha' gang //
NK039(ti)020:258: sngon tshe srid pa'i dbang mo che //
NK039(ti)020:259: de ltar dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)020:260: lha srin kun gyi gshed byed ma //
NK039(ti)020:261: skye 'gro kun gyi bdud bcod ma //
NK039(ti)020:262: dgra bo yongs kyi snying 'byin ma //
NK039(ti)020:263: bgegs dpung thal ba brlag mdzad ma //
NK039(ti)020:264: chos nyid ngang la klong dag ma //
NK039(ti)020:265: thugs dang 'gal ba mdzod par gsol //
NK039(ti)020:267: ma mo'i khrag mdos las bzlog pa'i smrang chen mo'i dabu'o //
NK039(ti)020:269: nga ni dbang phyug chen mo ste //
NK039(ti)020:270: khams gsum srid gsum mnga' bdag mo //
NK039(ti)020:271: nga ni khro rgyal kun gyi rje //
NK039(ti)020:272: nga ni ma mo kun gyi yab //
NK039(ti)020:273: khams gsum snying khrag dwangs ma'i bdag /
NK039(ti)020:274: 'gro ba'i don la rab brtson phyir //
NK039(ti)020:275: yon bdag skyabs gsol thugs rjes bzung //
NK039(ti)020:276: de ring bdud la mi gcig bslu //
NK039(ti)020:277: de ring btsan la thar gcig dgyes //
NK039(ti)020:278: de ring khams su dbang du bsdu //
NK039(ti)020:279: de ring srid gsum zil gyis mnan //
NK039(ti)020:280: de ring ma mo'i khram g.yas gyis //
NK039(ti)020:281: srid pa'i rgyal mo gnas 'dir byon //
NK039(ti)020:282: rims kyi bdag mo da tshur byon //
NK039(ti)020:283: ma mo srid pa'i rgyal mo 'di //
NK039(ti)020:284: 'od srung bstan pa nub kha ru //
NK039(ti)020:285: rgyal ba sh+aakya thub pa dang //
NK039(ti)020:286: smon lam dus gcig btab pa'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:287: sh+aakya thub pa'i bstan pa la //
NK039(ti)020:288: 'gro ba'i don du rab tu brtson //
NK039(ti)020:289: sku ni kun tu bzang mo la //
NK039(ti)020:290: gsung ni sgra dbyangs tshig las 'das //
NK039(ti)020:291: thugs ni smra bsam brjod las 'das //
NK039(ti)020:292: che mchog 'bar ba'i sku gsung thugs //
NK039(ti)020:293: gsang ba'i mkha' la phyed phyun tsam //
NK039(ti)020:295: 'byung ba'i rgyal mo thams cad bskyed //
NK039(ti)020:297: nad kyi skal ba gtong zhing byung //
NK039(ti)020:298: skye 'chi rtsad gcod bde klong thugs su chud //
NK039(ti)020:299: 'byung ba kun gyi cha snyoms ma //
NK039(ti)020:300: thig le dbyings la bskyed pa'i yum gcig ma //
NK039(ti)020:301: kun gyis yum bdag ma mo 'dir gshegs shig /
NK039(ti)020:302: srid pa'i rgyal mo 'dir gshegs shig /
NK039(ti)020:303: glud 'di srid pa'i rgyal mos bzhengs //
NK039(ti)020:304: de ring bzlog bsgyur dus la bab //
NK039(ti)020:305: nad kyi bdag mo ci phyir du //
NK039(ti)020:306: rims kha de ni mi chod dam //
NK039(ti)020:307: dpal gyi bdag mo ci phyir du //
NK039(ti)020:308: dal kha de ni mi bzlog gam //
NK039(ti)020:309: rims kyi bdag mo ci phyir du //
NK039(ti)020:310: rims kha de ni mi bsgyur ram //
NK039(ti)020:311: zlog cig dmar chen gtor mas bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:312: sgyur cig ltas ngan yu sdig bsgyur //
NK039(ti)020:313: kye ma cig srid pa'i rgyal mo ste //
NK039(ti)020:315: khyod kyis bdud la bka' nan chung //
NK039(ti)020:316: btsan btsun dmu la bka' nan chung //
NK039(ti)020:317: ma brgya dang sgral tshig g.yon pa nas //
NK039(ti)020:318: mi gshed drag po'i gzhung byas nas //
NK039(ti)020:319: thog dmar bu yug char du 'beb //
NK039(ti)020:320: bka' la 'das na dmyal thag gcod //
NK039(ti)020:321: khrag mda' bu yug char du 'beb //
NK039(ti)020:322: bzlog byed ma'i dus la bab //
NK039(ti)020:323: dal kha bzlog cing bsgyur byed ma //
NK039(ti)020:324: sngags kyi thun zor bzlog byed ma //
NK039(ti)020:325: byang bstims dang ni sku dug dang /
NK039(ti)020:326: lo kag dang ni zla kag dang //
NK039(ti)020:327: zhag kag dang ni za kag dang //
NK039(ti)020:328: ging kag dang ni gshed bzhi dang //
NK039(ti)020:329: bdud g.yos dang ni sri langs dang //
NK039(ti)020:330: mtshan ltas ngan pa bzlog tu gsol //
NK039(ti)020:331: gtso mo'i rbab zor rab tu drag /
NK039(ti)020:332: yung kar rbab bsgril khra la la //
NK039(ti)020:333: gnod byed bar chad bgegs zor bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:334: dal kha chod la rims kha bsgyur //
NK039(ti)020:335: zlog cig dmar chen sgyur cig ltas ngan h'u /
NK039(ti)020:336: nga ni dbang phyug chen po ste //
NK039(ti)020:337: khams gsum srid gsum mnga' bdag rje //
NK039(ti)020:338: 'gro ba'i don la rab tu brtson //
NK039(ti)020:339: yon bdag skyabs gsol thugs rjes bzung //
NK039(ti)020:341: rims kyi bdag mo spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)020:342: bsgyur byed ma cig spyan 'dren no //
NK039(ti)020:343: bzlog byed ma cig spyan 'dren nas //
NK039(ti)020:344: de ring bzlog bsgyur dus la bab //
NK039(ti)020:345: glud bdag chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)020:346: khro rgyal kun gyi yum cig ma //
NK039(ti)020:347: ma mo kun gyi bya ma rta //
NK039(ti)020:348: bsten byed kun gyi yang rje mo //
NK039(ti)020:349: 'gro ba kun gyi srog bdag mo //
NK039(ti)020:350: byang shar mtshams nas gnas bcas shing //
NK039(ti)020:351: bswe'i sku mkhar gru bzhi la //
NK039(ti)020:352: logs bzhi de ni mchong las byas //
NK039(ti)020:353: gser sbrul de ni khra bo la //
NK039(ti)020:354: gnyen po de la sbrul mi 'gos //
NK039(ti)020:355: zur bzhi de ni mchong la byas //
NK039(ti)020:356: lcags dang 'chong zur smug po la //
NK039(ti)020:357: gnyen te de la sbrul mi khrid //
NK039(ti)020:358: kha bad mtsho rog g.yu la byas //
NK039(ti)020:359: g.yu 'od de ni sngon po la //
NK039(ti)020:360: de la mtho ste bya mi lding //
NK039(ti)020:361: 'gram bzhi de ni lcags la byas //
NK039(ti)020:362: lcags 'gram de ni sngon po la //
NK039(ti)020:363: de la zhabs su byil mi 'dzul //
NK039(ti)020:364: tha ma lcags ri 'bar bas brgyan //
NK039(ti)020:365: de yang dbus su bsgrod pa la //
NK039(ti)020:366: de la gnyen te bdud mi gda' //
NK039(ti)020:367: sku mkhar de'i nang dbus nas //
NK039(ti)020:368: rin chen shel gyi sgo btsugs shing //
NK039(ti)020:369: mi ro rta ro'i khri steng du //
NK039(ti)020:370: gshin rje'i lcam gcig bzhugs pa ni //
NK039(ti)020:371: sku mdog mthing nag ral pa can //
NK039(ti)020:372: dbang rtags khrag gi thig le brgyan //
NK039(ti)020:373: chibs su drel rta rkang gsum bcib //
NK039(ti)020:374: d+r+wa ba dgu'i stong la can //
NK039(ti)020:375: nyin zhing khyo dgu rkung su byed //
NK039(ti)020:376: bzlog go dmar chen bsgyur ro ltas ngan b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)020:377: ma cig dpal ldan re ma ti //
NK039(ti)020:378: re sde gong nyag man chad dang //
NK039(ti)020:379: bdud rigs gtogs pa thams cad dang //
NK039(ti)020:380: bskor bskor zhung zhung phyag byas nas //
NK039(ti)020:381: jo mo de ni spyan mi bzang //
NK039(ti)020:382: phyag len mi ster khro tshul ston //
NK039(ti)020:383: dmar chen gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)020:384: bdud kyi lag nas mi bla bslu //
NK039(ti)020:385: skyes bu lung btsan man chad dang //
NK039(ti)020:386: phyi nang mtha' yas thams cad kyi //
NK039(ti)020:387: bskor bskor zhung zhung jo mo de phyag len mi
NK039(ti)020:388: ster dmar chen gtor ma btsan gyi lag nas mi
NK039(ti)020:389: bla bslu gnam lha dkar po man chad dang //
NK039(ti)020:390: nag mo grong rgyug yan chad kyi //
NK039(ti)020:391: bskor bskor zhung zhung jo mo de ni phyag lan dmar chen rgyal po'i lag nas mi bla bslu //
NK039(ti)020:392: bdud kyi rgyal po man chad dang //
NK039(ti)020:393: dur sri srin mo yan chad dang //
NK039(ti)020:394: bgegs phran grong rgyug yan chad kyi //
NK039(ti)020:395: bskor bskor zhung zhung jo mo de ni phyag lan
NK039(ti)020:396: mi dmar chen gtor ma bgegs kyi lag nas mi
NK039(ti)020:397: bla bslu // rgyu sbyor yon bdag 'khor bcas kyi //
NK039(ti)020:398: dus la bab pa'i tshe zad kyang //
NK039(ti)020:399: lo gsum bar du bshol thob cig /
NK039(ti)020:400: de ring bzlog bsgyur dus la bab //
NK039(ti)020:401: khyod kyis bzlog na rbab kyang bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:402: mi thub pa ni cig kyang med //
NK039(ti)020:403: khyod kyis bkyag nas 'brug kyang khyog //
NK039(ti)020:404: mi khyog pa ni ci lta bu //
NK039(ti)020:405: khyod ni bzung nas glog kyang bzung //
NK039(ti)020:406: mi zun bya ba gang yang med //
NK039(ti)020:407: bzlog bsgyur mdzad pa'i dus la bab //
NK039(ti)020:408: bzlog cig dmar chen gtor mas bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:409: bsgyur ro ltas ngan cho 'phrul bsgyur //
NK039(ti)020:410: ma mo'i zor kha brda la re //
NK039(ti)020:411: ma mo'i zor sna dgra la rgyob //
NK039(ti)020:412: yon bdag glud byol dgra la byol //
NK039(ti)020:414: ser sna'i phyi 'gyod ma btang cig /
NK039(ti)020:415: ma mo'i rta bro kyi li li //
NK039(ti)020:416: drag po'i bshug glu kyu ru ru //
NK039(ti)020:417: ma mo'i zor kha brda la re //
NK039(ti)020:418: bzang na bzang gsum sha ra ra //
NK039(ti)020:419: ngan na ngan gsum kyi li li //
NK039(ti)020:420: lnga nub drug nub tshun tshad du //
NK039(ti)020:421: dus na rgyal ba'i mnga' bdag mdzad //
NK039(ti)020:422: gsum nub bzhi nub tshun chad du //
NK039(ti)020:423: gsang sngags ngas kyang ma bzlog ste //
NK039(ti)020:424: ma mo'i skyog kha dgra la ston //
NK039(ti)020:425: dpal ldan gnyan gyi re ma ti //
NK039(ti)020:426: sngon tshe rgyal bas 'di skad gsung //
NK039(ti)020:427: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK039(ti)020:428: dge ba phun sum tshogs par bya //
NK039(ti)020:429: rang gi sems ni yongs su dul //
NK039(ti)020:430: gzhan gyis sems ni dkrugs mi bya //
NK039(ti)020:431: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK039(ti)020:432: da lta ngas kyang de skad bshad //
NK039(ti)020:433: yon bdag drin len chud ma gsan //
NK039(ti)020:434: dbang phyug nga'i bka' ma bcag /
NK039(ti)020:435: yon bdag 'khor dang bcas pa yi //
NK039(ti)020:436: dus la bab pa tshe zad kyang //
NK039(ti)020:437: lo gsum bar du shol thob cig /
NK039(ti)020:439: dpal ldan 'khor bcas dus la bab //
NK039(ti)020:440: so sor mthun pa'i rdzas bsogs pa //
NK039(ti)020:441: snying gi rtsa lags ma nyams dang //
NK039(ti)020:442: mi dbang 'bras bu smin pa'i sha //
NK039(ti)020:443: 'chi kha'i mtshal thig dmar po la //
NK039(ti)020:444: nya yi rgyu khrag skam po dang //
NK039(ti)020:445: mthun pa'i rdzas chen khyed la 'bul //
NK039(ti)020:446: ma cig sku la mthun rdzas 'bul ba ni //
NK039(ti)020:447: chibs su drel nag kha dkar dang //
NK039(ti)020:448: nas 'bras dang ni gro dang til //
NK039(ti)020:449: drel chung gzhon nu'i sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)020:450: btso dang zhu mkhan sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)020:451: ma cig mthun pa'i rdzas su bzhes //
NK039(ti)020:452: yul ni lho kha mon kha'i tshul //
NK039(ti)020:453: ma cig skyin mthing ya ma skyong //
NK039(ti)020:454: chibs su sha ba dkar mo bcibs //
NK039(ti)020:455: ram dang rgya skags mtshal dang spos //
NK039(ti)020:456: mdzes pa'i me tog sna tshogs dang //
NK039(ti)020:457: sha ba yu mo'i sha khrag dang //
NK039(ti)020:458: ma cig mthun rdzas bzhes su gsol //
NK039(ti)020:459: mi dang glud du da rjes shig /
NK039(ti)020:461: rdo rje gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)020:462: mang po dri za'i bka' bsgyur ma //
NK039(ti)020:463: bdag cag rdo rje spun rnams dang //
NK039(ti)020:464: de ring rgyu 'byor yon bdag la //
NK039(ti)020:465: gaza'i thog rgyug byung la re //
NK039(ti)020:466: bzlog go dmar chen gtor mas bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:467: bsgyur ro ltas ngan cho 'phrul bsgyur //
NK039(ti)020:468: sngon gyi bka' bsgyur dam can ma //
NK039(ti)020:469: do nub bzlog bsgyur dus la bab //
NK039(ti)020:471: rin chen gar gyi dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)020:472: ming po gshin rje'i bka' bsgyur la //
NK039(ti)020:473: bdag cag rdo rje de ring rgyu 'byor gshin rje'i
NK039(ti)020:474: dal ka bzlog go dmar chen bsgyur ro ltas ngan
NK039(ti)020:475: sngon gyi bka' bsgyur do nub bzlog b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)020:476: pad+ma rigs kyis dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)020:477: ming po klu'i bdag cag de ring klu'i dal kha
NK039(ti)020:478: bzlog go dmar bsgyur ro sngon gyis do nub bzlog
NK039(ti)020:479: b+h+yo / las kyi rigs kyis dbang phyug ma //
NK039(ti)020:480: ming po gnod sbyin bdag cag de ring gnod sbyin
NK039(ti)020:481: bzlog go dmar bsgyur ro sngon gyis do nub bzlog
NK039(ti)020:482: b+h+yo / dbang phyug phra men rgya mtsho la //
NK039(ti)020:483: he len gcig khyab bka' bdag cag de ring gnod
NK039(ti)020:484: sbyin dal yam bzlog go bsgyur ro sngon gyis do
NK039(ti)020:485: nub bzlog b+h+yo / e ka tsa ti thal mdog ma //
NK039(ti)020:486: skos rje drang dkar dam can ma //
NK039(ti)020:487: bdag cag de ring skos kyi byan mas bskul la re //
NK039(ti)020:488: bzlog go bsgyur ro sngon gyis do nub b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)020:489: e ka tsa ti ral gcig ma //
NK039(ti)020:490: re sde mgo nyag bka' bsgyur dam can ma //
NK039(ti)020:491: bdag cag de ring bdud kyi khram la thob ta re //
NK039(ti)020:492: bzlog go bsgyur ro sngon gyis do nub b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)020:493: nyi ma stong gi thod phreng ma //
NK039(ti)020:494: gnam thil dkar po'i bka' bsgyur la //
NK039(ti)020:495: bdag cag rdo rje rgyu 'byor yon rgyal po'i gdan la bab la re //
NK039(ti)020:496: bzlog go bsgyur ro sngon gyis do nub b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)020:497: nam mkha'i khams nas thog 'beb ma bar thil khra bo'i bka' bsgyur ma //
NK039(ti)020:498: bdag cag rgyu 'byor blon po'i khyim du bab la re //
NK039(ti)020:499: bzlog go bsgyur ro sngon gyis do nub b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)020:500: sa bdag chen mo pad+ma phreng //
NK039(ti)020:501: sa thil nag po'i bka' bdag cag rgyu 'byor yul phyir 'byung po bab la re //
NK039(ti)020:502: bzlog go bsgyur ro sngon gyis do nub b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)020:503: btsan gyi gla ba ro dang btsan //
NK039(ti)020:504: btsan gyi rta bab shor la re //
NK039(ti)020:505: bzlog go bsgyur ro sngon gyis do nub b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)020:506: gnam la ya za sman gcig ma //
NK039(ti)020:507: ming po gaza'i bka' bsgyur la //
NK039(ti)020:508: bdag cag rdo rje spun rnams la //
NK039(ti)020:509: rgyu 'byor gaza'i dal ka bab la re //
NK039(ti)020:510: bzlog go bsgyur ro sngon gyis do nub b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)020:511: lha mo nag mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)020:512: nor bu bzang po'i cho 'phrul bka' //
NK039(ti)020:513: bdag cag rgyu 'byor sngon gyis do nub b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)020:514: dpal ldan gnyen gyi re ma ti //
NK039(ti)020:515: khyod ni nang gi srung ma ste //
NK039(ti)020:516: dam rdzas bdud rtsi gtor ma 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)020:517: ma mo 'khrugs pa'i thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK039(ti)020:518: bdag cag rgyu 'byor g.yas bdud g.yas su byol kha bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:519: g.yon bdud g.yon du byol kha bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:520: bu tsha chung sri'i byol kha bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:521: sngon gyis gdug byed byol kha bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:522: pha tshan rgyab 'dre byol ma tshan stong 'dre'i byol
NK039(ti)020:523: kha bdud kyis khrom zur byol btsan gyi bang zur
NK039(ti)020:524: ma mo'i nad rims ban+d+he'i sngags zor bon po'i dzo
NK039(ti)020:525: zor bram ze'i ngan sngags rku dug byad stems byol
NK039(ti)020:526: lo kag zla kag zhag kag king kang gshed bzhi'i
NK039(ti)020:527: byol mtshan ngan ltas ngan byol bdag dang yon bdag
NK039(ti)020:528: 'khor bcas la // pho bdud dal kha g.yas su bsgyur //
NK039(ti)020:529: mo bdud dal kha g.yon du bsgyur //
NK039(ti)020:530: spyi bdud dal kha mkha' la bsgyur //
NK039(ti)020:531: dal kha bsgyur la rims kha bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:532: yon bdag glud byol dgra la bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:533: sdang ba'i dgra la byol kha ston //
NK039(ti)020:534: gnod pa'i bgegs la byon kha ston //
NK039(ti)020:535: sdang ba'i dgra la btang ba'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:536: yul du mkhar zhing rgya grong 'dzin //
NK039(ti)020:537: chung ma'i zhing yang gtan mi skye //
NK039(ti)020:538: bu tsha'i rigs rgyud rtsad nas chod //
NK039(ti)020:539: gnod pa'i bgegs la btang ba'i tshe //
NK039(ti)020:540: gnam lha dkar po khrag tu skyugs //
NK039(ti)020:541: byi na ya ga 'dar zhing brgyal //
NK039(ti)020:542: da ni bzlog bsgyur dus la bab //
NK039(ti)020:543: dmag gi rgyal mo chen mo b+h+yo //
NK039(ti)020:544: dgra bla'i rgyal mo chen mo b+h+yo //
NK039(ti)020:545: dar nag stong gi tshogs dang b+h+yo //
NK039(ti)020:546: le brgan stong gi rgyal mo b+h+yo //
NK039(ti)020:548: da ni ma mo'i khram sna bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:549: rims nad yams kyi khram sna bzlog /
NK039(ti)020:552: dus la bab pa'i tshe zad kyang //
NK039(ti)020:553: lo gsum bar du bshol thob cig /
NK039(ti)020:554: dbang phyug ma'i bka' ma bcag /
NK039(ti)020:555: yon bdag drin lan chud ma gsan //
NK039(ti)020:556: bka' dang dam la ma 'da' zhig /
NK039(ti)020:557: 'dod pa'i dngos grub bdag la stsol //
NK039(ti)020:558: ci bsam don rnams 'grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)020:559: dpal ldan lha mo'i bskang mdos 'khrug bcos zhes bya ba ni /
NK039(ti)020:561: mi shi ba thams cad la 'di bya'o //
NK039(ti)020:562: khyad par du nad yams dar ba'i dus su la
NK039(ti)020:563: 'di byas nas rgya nad thams cad ma mo'i kha
NK039(ti)020:564: rlangs yin / don 'di la brtson par bya'o //
NK039(ti)020:565: myur du phan par snang gsungs so //
